en el terminal:
pip install streamlit

python -m streamlit hello

streamlit run hello.py

python -m streamlit hello



Virtual env:
python -m venv .venv

Activar virt. env:
macOS/Linux: source .venv/bin/activate
Windows (Command Prompt): .venv\Scripts\activate.bat

Instalar streamlit:
pip install streamlit
	
streamlit run your_app_name.py
